$ Windows: action center
@ action center


{ Opening the action center

  The → Windows/keyboard-shortcuts[keyboard shortcut] to open the action center is `windows+a`.

  Alaternatively, it can also be opened with the balloon like symbol on the → Windows/Appearance/Taskbar/notification-area (which itself is located on the
  right end of the → Windows/Appearance/Taskbar):
  gh|Windows-Pics|/Appearance/action-center/notification-area.png||

}

sa:
  → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/ActionCenterCPL_dll[`ActionCenterCPL.dll`]

  → Windows/registry/tree/HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE/Software/Microsoft/Windows/CurrentVersion/ActionCenter[`HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\ActionCenter`]
